Wani jam'iyyar siyasa a Wales ta ce kungiyar ta "mai son kai" ne game da sauya sunan, amma ta lura cewa MWP za a iya maye gurbin ta da karamin sauyawar kalmomi.
A wannan yanayin, a yaren Welsh ana furta haruffan w daidai da yadda ake furta haruffan u a yaren Yorkshire.
A halin yanzu hukumar majalisar dokokin da ke shirya dokokin game da sauya sunan ta ce: "Kowane mai bayar da rahoto zai yanke hukunci na karshe game da abin da ake kira 'yan majalisar, hakika zai zama batun 'yan majalisar".
