Jihohi 18 da kuma District of Columbia suna goyon bayan sabuwar manufar Amurka ta kalubalanci doka da ke hana ba da mafaka ga wadanda suka tsere daga gangami ko wadanda suka sha wahala daga tashin hankali a gida.
Wakilan jihohi 18 da kuma gundumomi sun shigar da takardar shaidar adalci a Washington a ranar Juma'a don tallafawa wani dan gudun hijira da ke kalubalantar manufar, NBC News ta ruwaito.
