Lauyoyin gwamnati da ke goyon bayan Grace sun bayyana Al Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala a matsayin kasashen da ke fuskantar matsaloli masu yawa na gangami da tashin hankali a gida, wanda ke haifar da yawan masu neman izinin 'yan gudun hijira na Amurka.
Sabon manufar neman mafaka ta Amurka ta yi watsi da wani hukunci na 2014 da hukumar neman mafaka ta ba da izinin baƙi marasa tsari da ke tserewa daga tashin hankali a gida su nemi mafaka.
