Jami'ai sun ce a ranar Juma'a, wata babbar girgizar kasa da tsunami a garin Indonesia sun kashe akalla mutane 384 kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai kara karuwa.
Lokacin da aka kashe sadarwa, jami'an ceto sun kasa samun wani bayani daga yankin Donggala Regency, yankin arewacin Palau, kusa da tsakiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5.
A Palau, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 da suka shiga cikin bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palau da Dongala, tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palau babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta tsakiya ne, wanda ke kan iyakar bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan mutanen da aka kiyasta a shekara ta 2017 na 379,800.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwa.
Dongala wani yanki ne na bakin teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, wanda ya mamaye fiye da kilomita 300 (180 mi).
A karkashin lardin, Regency yana da kimanin mutane 299, wanda ya kai 200 a shekarar 2017.
Babban tushen tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi na tsakiya shine kifi da noma, musamman a yankunan bakin teku na Dongala.
Har ila yau, ma'adinai na nickel suna da mahimmanci a lardin, amma suna da yawa a Morovaly a bakin tekun da ke sabanin Max Sulawesi.
A cewar hukumar rage bala'i ta Indonesia, tsunami ya addabi Palau da Dongala sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami a yankin Dongala ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane fiye da 200 da kuma lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje.
A shekarar 1996 kuma tsunami ya afku a yammacin yankin Dongala inda mutane tara suka mutu.
Indonesia tana zaune a cikin Pacific Ring of Fire a matsayin ƙasa mai girgizar ƙasa kuma tana fuskantar girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, tsunami ya afku a kasashe 14 a arewacin Sumatra, a yankin yammacin lardin Ake, Indonesia, inda mutane 226,000 suka mutu a bakin tekun Tekun Indiya, rabin su a Ake.
2005: Wani mummunan girgizar ƙasa ya afku a yammacin Sumatra a watan Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias a gabar Sumatra.
2006: Tsunami mai girma 6.8 ya afku a tsibirin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, inda ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya fashe a gabar kudu inda ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.6 ta afku a yankin dake kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5 a tsibirin Mentawai a gabar Sumatra ta afkawa yankin, wanda ya haddasa tsunami mai girma har zuwa mita 10, wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da dama kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar ruwa mai zurfi a AK ya afkawa Pidi Jaya Regency, wanda ya haifar da lalacewa da tserewa saboda ya sa mutane su tuna da mummunan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 2004.
A wannan karon babu tsunami, amma sama da mutane 100 ne suka mutu sakamakon rushewar gine -gine ko gine -gine.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a tsibirin yawon shakatawa na Lombok na Indonesia ta lalata komai, inda aka kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasa ta lalata dubban gine -gine kuma ta hana dubban masu yawon buɗe ido taimako na ɗan lokaci.
