Masu gabatar da kara a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa mai wuya ga Saffulo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas -- hukuncin kisa da ba a saba yi a jihar ba tun 1953 don aikata laifi na tarayya.
